QuestData.Title: Sound the Alarm
QuestData.Description: Sirens are nothing but trouble! All they do is capture our men, never to be seen again. How is anybody supposed to get their goods to Boralus quickly with them around?$b$bSince you're already going down there... mind culling their numbers a bit?
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill $1oa Wailing Sirens in Fogcliff Strand.
